text: "New York, New York" is a 2001 debut single by Ryan Adams and is the leading single from his second studio album Gold. It went to number 53 in the United Kingdom and number 83 in the Netherlands. It was nominated for a Grammy Award in 2002. == Track listing == # "New York, New York" # "Mara Lisa" # "From Me to You" ==References== Category:2001 songs Category:Debut singles Category:Country songs Category:Ryan Adams songs
